{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act29side", "eventName": "崔林特爾梅之金", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "ZT-7", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "協奏曲“復活” ", "storyInfo": "薇薇安娜、費德里科與黑鍵一起進入這片不存在於現實的空間——“荒域”。阿爾圖羅發現自己無法在荒域中演奏，被老巫妖重創。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "44_i10", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "憲……醫生很快就過來了。", "name": "薇薇安娜"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳、咳咳……", "name": "珂拉"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薇薇安娜，你在哭嗎？", "name": "珂拉"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我好像沒有力氣為你擦眼淚了。", "name": "珂拉"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "薇薇安娜"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，真是個太過敏感、太過善良的孩子。", "name": "珂拉"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我常常想起我們第一次見面的情形……", "name": "珂拉"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從崔林特爾梅趕到施彤領，把你從沃爾納的高塔接出來。你縮在車後座，緊緊抱著並不大的行李箱，頭輕輕靠在我的胸口。", "name": "珂拉"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在害怕離開父親嗎？咳，她在對接下來卡西米爾的異鄉生活感到恐懼嗎？我當時這麼想著。", "name": "珂拉"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但薇薇安……你只是試圖壓低身子，以免自己引人注目的角被看見，暴露行蹤，為沃爾納帶去麻煩。", "name": "珂拉"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實當時已是後半夜，偌大的選帝侯高塔群，沒有誰會察覺到一輛車的離開。", "name": "珂拉"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳，你當時還那麼小……", "name": "珂拉"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不記得了。", "name": "薇薇安娜"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，你記得。", "name": "珂拉"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子，你可以抱怨、可以責怪、可以失望、可以後悔、可以憤恨，咳，你都可以……然後才能……", "name": "珂拉"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我真的不想……您離開……", "name": "薇薇安娜"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我只有您了。", "name": "薇薇安娜"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我……再好好“看一看”你。", "name": "珂拉"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡，我在這裡。", "name": "薇薇安娜"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真慶幸，我看不清你現在的表情……", "name": "珂拉"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你值得過上更好的生活，薇薇安娜……如果真有的話……", "name": "珂拉"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g10_endlessspiral", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#7$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女皇塔再高，也不至於沒有盡頭。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "旋梯在眼前鋪開，但方向似乎被未知而不可逆的力量撕扯，她明明一直在前進，卻始終停留在原地。"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薇薇安娜有些疲憊，而人在疲憊時更容易察覺到自己的失去。"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……就像她二十二年的人生。"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstprun", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼了，是迷路了嗎？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薇薇安娜抬起頭。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一個年輕的卡普里尼女性。她看著自己，臉上寫滿好奇和關切。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也怪我跑得太急，撞到了你。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有關係。", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#2$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，你的臉色很差，還好嗎？", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是，在想一些事情。", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#3$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您對這裡很熟悉嗎？", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#10$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯嗯，我就住在這附近。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那請問，前面究竟通向哪裡？", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#10$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，你不是自己來的嗎？", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一條路通向哪裡，完全取決於你想去哪裡啊。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了你小心點，我得走了。", "name": "溫柔的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#5$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstprun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想去哪裡……", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#7$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "40,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薇薇安娜的手指撫過身側的扶手，厚厚的灰塵下，赭紅色的漆覆蓋住烏提卡家族的紋樣，鮮豔得彷彿是昨天才剛刷上去。"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巫王。", "name": "薇薇安娜"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想起讀過的那本歷史小說《餘燼》。"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巫王即位之初，交給了匠人們一張圖紙，上面畫著一座萊塔尼亞前所未有的巍峨巨構——“始源之塔”。"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "單單看圖紙，就彷彿正站在它的基座前喘不過氣來。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巫王對始源之塔的要求極其嚴苛，細緻到了每一根欄杆的用料和上漆，它們必須保證永不褪色。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它將是萊塔尼亞的唯一象徵。"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wtchkgtwrfll", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#10$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼回事，“始源之角”已經完全降臨？", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#10$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可剛剛那位女士……", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#10$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薇薇安娜猛然反應了過來。"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛經過的卡普里尼，像是崔林特爾梅外城區最常見的那種年輕人，正是充滿活力的年紀，忙碌但不知疲倦，聲音裡有一杯新茶的熱氣。"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是在女皇塔，還是“始源之角”，她都不應該出現。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薇薇安娜連忙回望，可對方早已失去了蹤影。"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薇薇安娜，那麼你呢？", "name": "薇薇安娜"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為什麼出現在這裡？", "name": "薇薇安娜"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為什麼回到萊塔尼亞？當年又為什麼會離開？", "name": "薇薇安娜"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你沒能見到父親最後一面，甚至沒能回到那座常年被雨水和青苔洇濕的高塔。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你看著珂拉在自己的懷裡死去，你沒能帶她離開這座被夕陽焚燒的城市。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你還能阻止什麼？你還能改變什麼？你還能，做到什麼？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "如果巫王並未真的死去，他就在這無盡螺旋的盡頭，難道自己要像那些瘋狂的信徒一樣，指望他為自己指點迷津嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "未免有些滑稽。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spirlstrsndlss", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#4$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "階梯依然在延伸……某個不起眼的拐角，薇薇安娜突然看見了一扇門。"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那扇她再熟悉不過的，小小的門。"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4098_vvana_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "薇薇安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4098_vvana_1#2$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g10_endlessspiral", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘗試在每個連接處左轉，以連續偏離方向來保證前進。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "失敗。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘗試下行。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g10_endlessspiral", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "四十五分鐘，仍未回到旋梯的底端。失敗。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科已經在女皇塔的旋梯上耗費了相當長的時間，又一次突破失敗後，他停下了腳步。"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從原理上說，法術是一種更為嚴謹的秩序。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雙子女皇不會起用罹患精神疾病的設計師來設計高塔，也沒有工匠能將這樣毫無章法的建築結構還原出來。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在路德維格大學奏鳴塔的經歷誤導了我的判斷……女皇塔內部正在發生的扭曲與術式無關。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“始源之角”已經覆蓋住了女皇塔，引發了空間異變？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿爾圖羅的琴聲也已經消失……", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunshot", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunshot", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunshot", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科稍作思索，隨即拔出守護銃，向著身前射擊。"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "銃的嘯聲響徹整個空間，但子彈本身卻似乎被無形之物抹去了……它們消失在了眼前。"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……！", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那邊的薩科塔先生！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_timestop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聲音響起的瞬間，費德里科又看見了那幾顆銃彈。它們的移動軌跡緩慢而清晰，像是石子漂過水面。漣漪擴散，水下的一切逐漸浮現。"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g12_multispace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunload", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$higherdimensionalspaces_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——", "name": "著急的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#3$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請你把銃收起來！", "name": "著急的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#3$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是……", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請你把銃收起來！", "name": "著急的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#4$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用複述，我已經聽清了。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本次任務中遇到的每個人都在強調這件事情。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為這是一件不需要強調的事情呀……崔林特爾梅和拉特蘭不一樣……", "name": "著急的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洛里斯以前老講拉特蘭的事情。他說薩科塔走在街道上，遇到討厭的建築會“炸一炸”，遇到喜歡的建築，會更迫不及待地“炸一炸”。", "name": "著急的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和揚還一直覺得他只是因為對家鄉印象不太好，所以老愛編些瞎話。", "name": "著急的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，請看看周圍。", "name": "著急的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_signlntrfrnc", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_signalInterference", "fade": "true", "fadetime": 1.5, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "崔林特爾梅是一座古城，可能某面牆某片瓦上，就有百年前某位藝術家喝醉後用法術刻上去的樂譜或者詩歌。", "name": "著急的女性"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "周圍……", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科很快適應了眼前的異象。"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假定此地即是“始源之角”，儲存“巫王遺產”的所在，即阿爾圖羅的最終目的地。"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那他不會認為銃彈足以擊碎某種壁障，將自己從那古怪的旋梯帶到這裡。"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科看著面前的女性。她面色慍怒，真的像一個制止遊客沒水準行為的正義市民。"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩科塔先生，不知道你能不能理解……請把銃收起來。", "name": "著急的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#4$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "容許我打斷一下。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們顯然並不是身處崔林特爾梅的街頭，但你似乎毫無察覺。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及，你剛才提到的“洛里斯”和“揚”，如果全名為“洛里斯·博爾丁”和“揚·許勒爾”……", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請告知我你的姓名和身份。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "著急的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤利婭……尤利婭·許勒爾。", "name": "著急的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#6$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g12_multispace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是……“始源之角”內部，巫王的死後之地？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是巫王……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別東張西望了，小薩科塔。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您追上來了……我並不意外。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵，倒是你，竟然敢攀著巫妖的絲線主動被“放逐”……真是給了我不少驚喜。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……巫王在哪裡？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死透了。不然呢？", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我應該能感受到他。他的法術、他的情感、他的意志……只要我……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿爾圖羅環顧四周，在這個空間裡，邊界彷彿並不存在，唯有種種難以名狀的光影在流動，彷彿混沌開翕時的呼吸。"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她將提琴立穩，手指輕輕按上琴弦，扣上琴弓，拉動。"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寂靜。"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弓與弦相交，卻沒有任何聲音發出來。這個她無比熟稔與自然的動作，在這一刻突然失去了意義。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，看起來你終於有所察覺了。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#2$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我無法演奏。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我丟失了……我的樂聲。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是“始源之角”的緣故？還是巫王設下的“規則”？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "狂妄。愚蠢。白癡。你頭頂的光環除了讓膚色看起來更白些，就沒有讓你的腦子更靈光一點嗎？", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#7$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以為這裡是什麼地方？", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#7$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫爾昏佐倫的棺材？薩爾貢那些走路漏沙的帕夏的藏寶窟？維多利亞童話裡老巫婆的魔法口袋？", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#7$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弗萊蒙特閣下……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（薩卡茲語）“千絲萬弦之始終”。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#3$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像是喃喃自語，弗萊蒙特用薩卡茲語吐出了一個異常生澀的詞彙。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又或者，用那傢伙起的名字，更符合你們的認知能力一些。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（萊塔尼亞語）“荒域”。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "荒域……？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你所見的，是“實在”的另一面，空間的另一個維度，它永恆變化，所有的規則和現實都將在被它碰觸到的瞬間湮滅。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巫妖一族在漫長的時間裡對其不過一窺。而赫爾昏佐倫窮盡畢生之力，也只是在這無盡的混沌裡吹出了這樣一個不穩定的泡泡。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿爾圖羅沒有回應弗萊蒙特的憤怒。她再次扣了扣琴弦，提琴依然沉默著。"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有失望，沒有恐懼，唯有疑惑。"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "強烈的疑惑在阿爾圖羅的臉上稍縱即逝。隨後，她抬起頭來，向著對方微笑。"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太好了。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#11$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巫王並不是依靠什麼秘法延續了自己的意志，而是在荒域中建起了自己的“行宮”。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#11$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這片空間是真實存在的，他也一定就在這個地方……只是我需要再走一段路，才能抵達他的王座。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#11$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你知道，在荒域中再次被“放逐”，會發生什麼嗎？", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1114_1#7$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_strngspllmgc", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$p_skill_darkholeborn", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陰影在生長……阿爾圖羅猛然警覺。"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在自己說話時，對方已經施放了巫術。以弗萊蒙特為圓心，那些絲弦般的陰影膨脹成粗壯的藤蔓，融進本就色彩曖昧的地面，蔓延過來。"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "腐朽的氣息開枝散葉，它最飽滿的形態，即是死亡與消逝。"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我還沒有得到答案。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須找回我的樂聲，我必須，演奏巫王。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還不能……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……死去。"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她願意在演奏的同時走向終點，卻無法接受自己消散在真相面前，寂靜之中。"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smoke_grenade", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_lightrain_loop", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陰影在一瞬間裂開，灰色的雨逆流而上，包裹了一切。"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 4.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 90.0, "randomness": 50.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-10", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_signlntrfrnc", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_signalInterference", "fade": "true", "fadetime": 1.5, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pipeorgantimer", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維恩大鐘樓響了！", "name": "巫王的樂手"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快走吧，去始源之塔，演奏就要開始了——", "name": "巫王的樂手"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新的樂曲，新的術式……為維杜尼亞抵禦天災和高盧人的火炮……", "name": "巫王的樂手"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫爾……赫爾昏佐倫……", "name": "巫王的樂手"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1", "bstart": 0.3, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1", "bstart": 0.3, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這裡的時空並不穩定。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是“放逐”誘發的嗎？", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，早在我們進入荒域之前就這樣了。赫爾昏佐倫的力量正在衰減。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1114_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“始源之角”……在加速崩塌。", "name": "弗萊蒙特"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#5$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "b", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g12_multispace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dimnlspamb", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tinnitus", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_dim_openeye", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.2, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……還活著？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛的旋律……又消失了……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她抓住了那一縷不同於周遭環境的聲響，拼命逃脫了“放逐”的絲線。"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而此刻那旋律化作了實體，從混沌中清晰地析出，落到她跟前。"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變成了……一個人。"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（混亂不清的聲響）", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您……是……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是您奏出了剛才的旋律，救了我……一命？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（混亂不清的聲響）", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1122_1#1$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是隨侍在巫王身側的……高塔術師嗎？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "PlayMusic", "